title: Sunshine yellow Flower Print Designer Blazer
story_description:
Story A fun and lightweight casual fabric for warm, sunny days. Tencel was one of the original
popular Aloha shirt fabrics, and for good reason—its smoothness and breathability made it one of the
most comfortable options available for residents of the steamy Hawaiian islands. This version’s 35s
single-ply plain weave construction creates a soft, beautiful drape, and it allows air to flow
easily through the fabric. Plus, Tencel is absorbent and cool to the touch, and polyester is very
quick to dry, so it’s perfect for warm weather. This Blazer offers our signature quality and
tailoring at an excellent value. Crafted of tencel in italy, and sold as fully finished separates to
make it easier to find your perfect fit. Two-button silhouette, notched lapels, Black buttons,
finished sleeve cuffs, besom chest pocket, convertible flap-welt waist pockets, center vent. Fully
lined interior features our signature piping and two interior pockets.Regent Fit: Our best-seller.
The perfect fit for just about everybody; fitted at the chest, shoulders and waist.
